    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's way harder than it looks. But just as weird. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arm Around! is a delightfully unhinged physics-based game, where you'll face the surreal challenge of controlling a disembodied arm using nothing but your mouse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/1d24ed3096a14752fedae97344b6c404.poster.avif?t=1765844020\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/1d24ed3096a14752fedae97344b6c404.webm?t=1765844020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/1d24ed3096a14752fedae97344b6c404.mp4?t=1765844020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crawl, jump, punch and arm around to physically interact with everything in sight as you stumble through Derechín’s wild, history-defining misadventures set throughout the 20th century.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/33b670fe8c5f89cffb4973f427f3ef07.poster.avif?t=1765844020\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/33b670fe8c5f89cffb4973f427f3ef07.webm?t=1765844020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/33b670fe8c5f89cffb4973f427f3ef07.mp4?t=1765844020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Not THAT weird controls</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even though the default controls aren't quite as normal as some would like, they were designed this way for a very special reason: you should be able to control every finger using the same finger in real life, and also be able to extend and contract the arm doing the same with yours! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/3ec96c4caee5c861692f7835a1acc4aa.poster.avif?t=1765844020\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/3ec96c4caee5c861692f7835a1acc4aa.webm?t=1765844020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/3ec96c4caee5c861692f7835a1acc4aa.mp4?t=1765844020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If that sounds like too much, there's also a simplified controls mode and you can also change the bindings to ones of your liking.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take the least amount of time possible!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oh, and one more thing, we're timing you, so if you feel like proving something you can always revisit any chapter and try to beat the clock.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/8233e568f1c311c53c319ea5e0cd9a4f.poster.avif?t=1765844020\" width=620 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/8233e568f1c311c53c319ea5e0cd9a4f.webm?t=1765844020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3072400/extras/8233e568f1c311c53c319ea5e0cd9a4f.mp4?t=1765844020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Best your friend's time to show off or even get to the top of the world-wide leaderboard to earn a well deserved (and very exclusive) achievement.  Do you have what it takes to get to the top? (Yes, this is a desperate call to the speedrunner community) <br><br>Long live the arm!</p>",
